                            <comment id="17222646" author="ychena" created="Thu, 29 Oct 2020 01:21:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kgyrtkirk&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kgyrtkirk&quot;&gt;kgyrtkirk&lt;/a&gt;, we cannot remove the ignore from it for the tests run fine when only run by itself, when I run the suite, it will have failures. My fixes in this Jira is just to add a new configurable property, it does not fix SSL existing issues in Hive. We may remove the ignore after we find the root cause of the issue and fix it. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
